The '''Absolutists''' were a group of [[Selonian/Legends|Selonians]], including the [[Overden]] allied with the [[Sacorrian Triad]], who sought to establish absolute Selonian independence using [[Selonia/Legends|Selonia's]] [[planetary repulsor]] as a weapon, which they eventually did against the [[Bakuran]] ship ''[[Watchkeeper]]''. They were constantly at odds with the [[Republicanists]], who saw membership in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] as beneficial to their world, and fought with them in an undeclared Selonian [[Corellian Crisis|Civil War]]. The [[Sacorrian Triad]] eventually helped dissolve the Absolutists.

